title: Watch Sampha, Jenn Wasner, More Sing Prince’s “Nothing Compares 2 U” in New Google Ad
text:
4 hrs ago Watch Sampha, Jenn Wasner, More Sing Prince’s “Nothing Compares 2 U” in New Google Ad Photos by Andrew Lipovsky/NBC/NBCU Photo Bank via Getty Images, Kevin Winter/Getty Images, Andrew Benge/Redferns via Getty Images 
Last night during the Grammys , a new ad for Google’s Pixel phone aired. The clip features several musicians paying tribute to Prince by singing “Nothing Compares 2 U”—the song he wrote that was made famous by Sinéad O’Connor. The spot includes performances from Sampha, Wye Oak and Flock of Dimes’ Jenn Wasner, Deer Tick’s John McCauley, Brandi Carlile, and others. Watch it below. Last night, Lil Yachty and Carly Rae Jepsen’s “It Takes Two” Target ad also premiered during the show. Artists In This Story
